result.formatted_address: Hong Kong, 沙田Wo Che Ha22號
result.name: Lung Wah Hotel

reviews.text: Place is the same as 30 years ago, but more run down. Food is mediocre.

There’s long way from the entrance to the restaurant decorating with a lot of red lanterns, it is beautiful, could be a good photo spot if u are looking for feeling of nostalgic Hong Kong. This restaurant is full of my childhood memory. But it became touristy now. I don’t want to be mean. However, the only-tasty-food is “roasted baby pigeon”. (I gave 4 stars for it) For the rest in the menu, I gave 1 star... the dishes came very fast, but usually were cold and tasteless. The service is so so.
The best "yu gap" in HK, a must go if you're a fan!
Best roasted pigeon! If you like pigeon it is a must when one visits Hong Kong. It's very close to 10000 Buddha temple
Their signature dish is really good and they have cream sodas.

result.adr_address: 香港沙田Wo Che Ha22號
result.name: 龍華酒店

reviews.text: 乳鴿好吃😋😋😋不過太貴了🤭🤭🤭
好好食啊乳鴿😍😍

迷ってしまって民家の隙間の階段を登ったり降りたり…途中dangerと書かれた看板があったりやっとたどり着けました。大通りから陸橋を渡ったらすぐなのにグーグルマップだとそのルートがでませんでした。

焼き蕎麦は美味しく、名物のハトもおいしかったです。お姉さんが食べやすいよう手袋をくれました。
トイレのペーパーは個室の前にとってから入る式なので注意
記憶已約2O年無到過，今再次光顧，全部情景都無大改變，乳鴿及鷄粥都算保持應有嘅水準，但價格就似乎同地方及佈置不成正比，其它小菜上桌時溫度已降曬溫啦，整體而言，無復當年嘅氣質，老人家及傷健人仕到此食飯更是一種考驗。
